nb apartmant unmarried man cave first residence after divorce

An unmarried man’s cave, especially his first, intended temporary,
residence after divorce.


nb meditation conscience morris adler prayer selfhood effect

Meditation takes us beyond the self.  Joining our little conscience to
the conscience of humanity, it gives our wishes the freedom to grow
large and broad and inclusive.―after Morris Adler

Our meditation is effective not when we are given what we seek,
but when we realize the motivation to become what we can be.
―ibid.
